      "content": "i guess. but it's hard to just \"exist\" when every day feels like such a massive chore. sometimes i think if i just stopped trying altogether... if i just drifted away or something... it wouldn't even be a tragedy. it would just be peace. do you think people actually find peace in just disappearing?",
